title: [Arahbella's Outfitting]
[Arahbella's General Store]
[Arahbella's Magic Shoppe]
description: A simple floral tapestry hangs on one of the brilliant cut-glass walls, and a modwir beam ceiling rises overhead.  An ornate archer statue sits in one corner of a dark-stained oak floor.  There is a gilded maple table on one side of the shop and a gilded maple cabinet on the other.
